⏱ During game loop
Every tick (e.g., 100ms):

Calculate current multiplier

For each bet:

if (bet.autoCashout && currentMultiplier >= bet.autoCashout) {
    cashout(bet)
}

When player clicks CASHOUT:
if (currentMultiplier < crashPoint && bet.status === "active") {
    bet.status = "cashed_out"
